title: Will psychics lose their ability after vaccine inoculation?
description: Answer (1 of 11): Will psychics lose their ability after vaccine inoculation? Can't lose what they never had to start with. Psychic powers do not exist. If they did, it would be painfully easy to actually demonstrate - but that has never, ever happened.
